{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/thymeleaf/180217_thymeleaf-layout-dialect/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"MHLab blog","author":"MHLab"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"dcc6a06c-6b00-5869-ba81-e76e3f53e7e2","excerpt":"주의 이 문건은 과거 Hexo 블로그 (2018-02-17) 에서 이동된 문서입니다. 시간이 지남에 따라 최신 기술과 다를 수 있으니 주의 바랍니다.  Thymeleaf에서 페이지 레이아웃을 도와주는... Spring boot…","html":"<h1 id=\"주의\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98\" aria-label=\"주의 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주의</h1>\n<h3 id=\"이-문건은-과거-hexo-블로그-2018-02-17-에서-이동된-문서입니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4-%EB%AC%B8%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%80-%EA%B3%BC%EA%B1%B0-hexo-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-2018-02-17-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%9D%B4%EB%8F%99%EB%90%9C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"이 문건은 과거 hexo 블로그 2018 02 17 에서 이동된 문서입니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이 문건은 과거 Hexo 블로그 (2018-02-17) 에서 이동된 문서입니다.</h3>\n<h4 id=\"시간이-지남에-따라-최신-기술과-다를-수-있으니-주의-바랍니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%9C%EA%B0%84%EC%9D%B4-%EC%A7%80%EB%82%A8%EC%97%90-%EB%94%B0%EB%9D%BC-%EC%B5%9C%EC%8B%A0-%EA%B8%B0%EC%88%A0%EA%B3%BC-%EB%8B%A4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EC%9C%BC%EB%8B%88-%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98-%EB%B0%94%EB%9E%8D%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"시간이 지남에 따라 최신 기술과 다를 수 있으니 주의 바랍니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>시간이 지남에 따라 최신 기술과 다를 수 있으니 주의 바랍니다.</h4>\n<hr>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/2cefc/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.306748466257666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"thumbnail\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/a6d36/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/222b7/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 163w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/ff46a/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 325w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/a6d36/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 650w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/e548f/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 975w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/3c492/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 1300w,\n/static/12069f57b0dd9b828b9ca52b4d9198ba/2cefc/thumbnail_thymeleaf.png 1400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h1 id=\"thymeleaf에서-페이지-레이아웃을-도와주는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#thymeleaf%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80-%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%95%84%EC%9B%83%EC%9D%84-%EB%8F%84%EC%99%80%EC%A3%BC%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"thymeleaf에서 페이지 레이아웃을 도와주는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Thymeleaf에서 페이지 레이아웃을 도와주는...</h1>\n<p>Spring boot로 개발을 하면 화면단 작업을 할 때 템플릿 엔진을 사용하게 됩니다.<br>\n<strong>Freemaker</strong>, <strong>JSP</strong>, <strong>Thymeleaf</strong>와 같은 <strong>텍스트 템플릿 엔진</strong>을 사용하거나 <strong>Tiles</strong>나 <strong>Sitemesh</strong>와 같은 <strong>레이아웃 템플릿 엔진</strong>을 함께 사용하여 화면단 개발을 하게 됩니다.</p>\n<p>이중 Thymeleaf에서는 공통적으로 사용하는 레이아웃을 작성하기 위해서는 <strong>thymeleaf-layout-dialect</strong>를 사용하면 좋습니다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ultraq/thymeleaf-layout-dialect\">Thymeleaf Layout Dialect Github</a> 페이지의 소개글을 간략하게 번역하자면 다음과 같습니다. (오류 번역이 있을 수 있습니다.)</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>타임리프에서 코드 재사용을 개선하기 위해 재사용이 가능한 레이아웃과 템플릿을 작성할 수 있도록 도와주는 라이브러리입니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>이 라이브러리는 <strong>Spring Boot 1.5.8.RELEASE</strong>의 <strong>spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf</strong> 스타터 의존성에 포함되어 있습니다.</p>\n<p>만약 Spring Boot starter를 사용하지 않거나, 다른 환경에서 사용하실 경우 <a href=\"https://ultraq.github.io/thymeleaf-layout-dialect/Installation.html\">공식 문서</a>의 설치 부분을 참고하시기 바랍니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"thymeleaf-layout-dialect의-간단한-사용-예제\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#thymeleaf-layout-dialect%EC%9D%98-%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C\" aria-label=\"thymeleaf layout dialect의 간단한 사용 예제 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>thymeleaf-layout-dialect의 간단한 사용 예제</h2>\n<p>공식 Github에 있는 예제를 기준으로 설명드리려 합니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"1-공통으로-사용할-layout-html-작성하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-layout-html-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"1 공통으로 사용할 layout html 작성하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 공통으로 사용할 Layout html 작성하기</h3>\n<p>먼저 컨텐츠 페이지에서 공통적으로 사용할 html을 작성합니다.<br>\n이 공통적으로 사용될 layout 파일명을 <strong>comm_layout.html</strong>이라 하겠습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>layout</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.ultraq.net.nz/thymeleaf/layout<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Layout page<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>common-script.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My website<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">layout:</span>fragment</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Page content goes here<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My footer<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">layout:</span>fragment</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>custom-footer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Custom footer here<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"2-실제-컨텐츠-페이지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%8B%A4%EC%A0%9C-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%90%EC%B8%A0-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"2 실제 컨텐츠 페이지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 실제 컨텐츠 페이지</h3>\n<p>컨텐츠 페이지는 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>layout</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.ultraq.net.nz/thymeleaf/layout<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">layout:</span>decorator</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>comm_layout<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content page<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content-script.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">layout:</span>fragment</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This is a paragraph from the content page<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">layout:</span>fragment</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>custom-footer<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        This is some footer content from the content page\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>컨텐츠 페이지에서 html의 태그 안에서 <strong>layout:decorator</strong> 속성이 있습니다.<br>\n해당 속성은 공통 레이아웃을 지정하는 속성으로 위 1번에서 사용한 레이아웃 파일명을 작성해줍니다.<br>\n확장자는 제거한 파일명을 적어주며, 실제 Spring Boot에서 사용하는 경로에 맞춰서 작성하게 됩니다.</p>\n<p>위 공통 레이아웃과 실제 컨텐츠를 적용한 페이지는 다음과 같은 <strong>결과물</strong>로 만들어지게 됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Content page<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>common-script.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content-script.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My website<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This is a paragraph from the content page<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>My footer<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This is some footer content from the content page<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위의 결과물을 보면 동작 원리나 방식에 대한 이해가 더 잘 될것입니다.<br>\n공통 레이아웃에 실제 컨텐츠 페이지를 덮어둔 형식으로 결과가 나오게 됩니다.<br>\n하지만 공통 레이아웃의 <strong>layout:fragment=</strong> 부분은 실제 컨텐츠 페이지의 선언된 내용으로 치환하게 됩니다.</p>\n<p><strong>thymeleaf-layout-dialect</strong>의 layout namespace를 사용하여 기본적인 방법을 알아봤습니다.</p>\n<p>Thymeleaf에서 실제로 <strong>dialect</strong>를 사용하는 예제는 <a href=\"https://elfinlas.github.io/thymeleaf/180216_thymeleaf-layout-dialect_exam/\">Thymeleaf에서 템플릿 형식으로 사용하기 포스팅</a>을 참고해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"toc\"><pre class=\"language-toc\"><code class=\"language-toc\"></code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98\">주의</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4-%EB%AC%B8%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%80-%EA%B3%BC%EA%B1%B0-hexo-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-2018-02-17-%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%9D%B4%EB%8F%99%EB%90%9C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\">이 문건은 과거 Hexo 블로그 (2018-02-17) 에서 이동된 문서입니다.</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#thymeleaf%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80-%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%95%84%EC%9B%83%EC%9D%84-%EB%8F%84%EC%99%80%EC%A3%BC%EB%8A%94\">Thymeleaf에서 페이지 레이아웃을 도와주는...</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#thymeleaf-layout-dialect%EC%9D%98-%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8%ED%95%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C\">thymeleaf-layout-dialect의 간단한 사용 예제</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%EA%B3%B5%ED%86%B5%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-layout-html-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">1. 공통으로 사용할 Layout html 작성하기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%EC%8B%A4%EC%A0%9C-%EC%BB%A8%ED%85%90%EC%B8%A0-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80\">2. 실제 컨텐츠 페이지</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Thymeleaf에서 thymeleaf-layout-dialect 소개","description":null,"date":"February 17, 2018","tags":["Thymeleaf"],"series":"Thymeleaf","previewImage":"thymeleaf_logo.png","isPrivate":null,"writer":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/thymeleaf/180216_thymeleaf-layout-dialect_exam/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Thymeleaf에서 템플릿 형식으로 사용하기(With thymeleaf-layout-dialect)","isPrivate":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/thymeleaf/180218_thymeleaf-if-exam/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Thymeleaf에서 if else 조건문 사용법","isPrivate":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"dcc6a06c-6b00-5869-ba81-e76e3f53e7e2","previousPostId":"144fb95c-7f65-54e7-8270-1650602b5f48","nextPostId":"9a0c2520-d90e-5e3a-9b5a-2f60eaf6d080"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}